{ What Are Pawn Structures?

Pawn structure literally refers to the pawn placement or pawn configuration in a position, disregarding all other pieces. Many different types of pawn structures can result from different openings. Some pawn structures can be identical or strikingly similar even though they come from completely different openings. }
